<p style="font-size:1.7rem; margin:0 0 1em;">Commander, welcome to the '''Azur Lane English Wiki'''!</p>
<p>{{L|''Azur Lane''|碧蓝航线|アズールレーン}} is a Chinese mobile game developed by Manjuu and Yongshi, published by [https://www.bilibili.com/ BiliBili] for both iOS and Android. Service began on May 25th, 2017 for iOS and June 2nd, 2017 for Android.</p>
<p>Japanese servers opened up on September 14th, 2017 for both iOS and Android.</p>
<p>English servers opened up for Open Beta on August 16th, 2018 for both iOS and Android, with official release on [[Recent News/EN/2019#May 20th 2019|May 20th, 2019]].</p>
